{"tid":796214,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"最近起左個server 有d問題","createTime":"2018-08-27T15:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T10:09:16.000Z","uid":82243,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a42a8bf8eed71697aa28cbbf1949caa6cd0e17","tid":796214,"uid":82243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有玩開linux<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟fg 最近整緊個project<br />\n開左個sever 用apache+php+mysql<br />\n整好晒啦諗住裝個cms系統落去<br />\n一入到去就話我/var/www/html冇寫入限權<br />\n明明我已經chmod -R 777 左<br />\n因為個安裝file我係經filezilla掉上去<br />\n掉左上去之後show左個owner同group係新user黎<br />\n除左個個新user可以係filezilla郁到之外，我轉左root:root係改permission都係permission denied<br />\n有冇巴打可以解答到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩del晒成個用wget重黎 <br />\n都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經全部都係drwxrwxrwx 但係system都係話我冇寫入權限"},{"pid":"d3dc9f64309033684c0a46ff0664231d54a54ca8","tid":796214,"uid":195904,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"會吾會系顯卡壞左牙？<br />\n聽講關事"},{"pid":"06c26d19cc3110a01ea6c94f9c3a84e8f0e1a2e0","tid":796214,"uid":82243,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"d3dc9f64309033684c0a46ff0664231d54a54ca8","tid":796214,"uid":195904,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"會吾會系顯卡壞左牙？<br />\n聽講關事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:20:12.000Z","msg":"顯卡好正常<br />\n仲食到雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca74fb122e567a77eb52901a4a63f8e07942fff7","tid":796214,"uid":23094,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"<code>sudo chmod -R 777 /</code>"},{"pid":"4481ca667300c875fd37cb550552f56e20ae4b58","tid":796214,"uid":44171,"